Subject: Ohio VW Event in May

Since it's Friday and all, and people have been
talking about camping, I'll drop this reminder:
The Ohio Valley Tribe Of the Full Moon Bus CLub
invites you to join us at the Fourth Annual VW Buses,
Bands, & Brews Event May 21-23 in Oregonia, Ohio (36
miles straight north of Cincinnati).
This years event will feature:
*Lotsa VW people
*Live music from "Man Made Moon"
http:/www.manmademoon.com & others
*Camping
*Homebrew beer\wine tasting
*Technical demos (including a homebrewing seminar!)
*World famous Full Moon Bus Club Breakfast Burritos
*BIG CAMP FIRES!
*AND MORE!
Here's the link to the event web page:
http://www.geocities.com/buses_n_boats
I hope you all can make it!

